G\" style=\"height:530px; width:813px\" /></p>\n\n<p>방화벽 메뉴에 들어갑니다.</p>\n\n<p></p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://server.musign.co.kr/include/ckeditor/upload/1589177136.PNG\" style=\"height:423px; width:1239px\" /></p>\n\n<p>규칙편집 버튼을 클릭합니다.</p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://server.musign.co.kr/include/ckeditor/upload/1589177148.PNG\" style=\"height:195px; width:769px\" /></p>\n\n<p>생성 버튼을 클릭합니다.</p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://server.musign.co.kr/include/ckeditor/upload/1589177158.PNG\" style=\"height:443px; width:599px\" /></p>\n\n<p>포트는 사용자지정 클릭 후&nbsp;원하는 포트를 기입합니다.</p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://server.musign.co.kr/include/ckeditor/upload/1589177170.PNG\" style=\"height:350px; width:596px\" /></p>\n\n<p>아이피 역시 허용할 아이피를 선택합니다.</p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://server.musign.co.kr/include/ckeditor/upload/1589177178.PNG\" style=\"height:312px; width:803px\" /></p>\n\n<p></p>\n\n<p>위 아래로 이동하여 우선순위를 정해줍니다.</p>\n\n<p>위에 있는것이 우선적이며,&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>예를들어 모든 아이피를 차단 한 후에 특정 아이피를 허용하면, 그 아이피는 접속이 거부됩니다.</p>\n\n<p></p>\n','20200511150903'),(34,'PHP 확장자 숨기기','<p>httpd.conf 에서</p>\n\n<p>&lt;Directory &quot;/var/www/html&quot;&gt; 부분의 옵션을</p>\n\n<p>Options -Indexes MultiViews FollowSymLinks</p>\n\n<p>이렇게 수정</p>\n','20200714162553'),(35,'TRACE METHOD 차단','<p>curl -v -X TRACE https://ad.lghellovision.net/</p>\n\n<p>명령어로 확인한다.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>TraceEnable Off&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>httpd.conf 에 이거 추가</p>\n','20200714162616'),(36,'Apache header php 정보 노출 제거','<p>/etc/php.ini 페이지에서</p>\n\n<p>expose_php = On&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>되어있는걸</p>\n\n<p>expose_php = Off 로 변경</p>\n','20200714162637'),(37,'Apache 정보노출 제거','<p>ServerTokens Full 이나 OS 로 되어있는것을</p>\n\n<p>ServerTokens Prod 로 변경<br />\n&nbsp;</p>\n','20200714162656'),(38,'Apache 특정 파일이나 디렉토리 접근제한','<p>&lt;Files ~ &quot;thanks&quot;&gt;<br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp; Order Deny,Allow<br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp; Deny from all<br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp; Allow from 127.0.0.1 220.118.83.174 125.57.206.101 125.57.206.11<br />\n&lt;/Files&gt;<br />\n&lt;Files ~ &quot;wp-login.php&quot;&gt;<br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp; Order Deny,Allow<br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp; Deny from all<br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp; Allow from 127.0.0.1 220.118.83.174 125.57.206.101 125.57.206.11<br />\n&lt;/Files&gt;<br />\n&nbsp;</p>\n','20200714162725'),(39,'iptables 특정 아이피만 허용','<p>iptables -A INPUT -p tcp -s 220.118.83.174 &nbsp;--dport 3306 -j ACCEPT<br />\niptables -A INPUT -p tcp --dport 3306 -j DROP;</p>\n\n<p><br />\niptables -nL 명령어로 확인<br />\nservice iptables save 명령어로 저장 (재부팅시 초기화되지않음)</p>\n','20200714162749'),(40,'HTTP Protocol 제한','<p>SSLProtocol -All +TLSv1.2<br />\nSSLCipherSuite ALL:!ADH:!EXPORT:!SSLv2:RC4+RSA:+HIGH:+MEDIUM:+LOW<br />\n&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>ssl.conf에 적용</p>\n','20200714162813'),(41,'사용자추가, 홈디렉토리변경, FTP 최상위 폴더 접근제한','<p>adduser abcd<br />\npasswd abcd</p>\n\n<p>//aws라면 비밀번호로 접속할수있도록 해줘야한다. 없으면 키파일필요.</p>\n\n<p>usermod -d /var/www/html/ abcd</p>\n\n<p>이건 홈디렉토리변경</p>\n\n<p><br />\n상위 디렉토리를 제한하려면</p>\n\n<p>vi /etc/vsftpd/vsftpd.conf</p>\n\n<p><br />\nchroot_local_user=YES<br />\n#chroot_list_enable=NO<br />\n# (default follows)<br />\n#chroot_list_file=/etc/vsftpd/chroot_list</p>\n\n<p>이렇게 설정 바꾸고</p>\n\n<p>service vsftpd restart</p>\n\n<p>그다음에 홈디렉토리를</p>\n\n<p>chmod 555 /var/www/html</p>\n\n<p>이렇게해서 권한을 변경해준다.<br />\n&nbsp;</p>\n','20200714163025'),(42,'JSP 웹서버 셋팅','<p>yum install -y httpd<br />\nsystemctl enable httpd<br />\nsystemctl start httpd</p>\n\n<p><br />\n- jdk<br />\nyum list | grep java 해가지고 리스트중에 설치</p>\n\n<p>yum -y install java-1.8.0-openjdk.x86_64</p>\n\n<p>java -version으로 확인</p>\n\n<p>- tomcat<br />\nhttp://tomcat.apache.org/ 페이지에서 tar.gz 파일 다운받기 설치파일 경로에 다운로드해두었음.<br />\naws 로 이동<br />\ntar -zxvf apache-tomcat-9.0.27.tar.gz 압축풀기<br />\nmv apache-tomcat-9.0.27 /usr/local<br />\ncd /usr/local/apache-tomcat-9.0.27/bin<br />\n./startup.sh</p>\n\n<p>(톰캣 폴더명 바꾸고싶으면 shutdown 해놓고 바꾸면될듯)</p>\n\n<p>-connector<br />\nhttps://tomcat.apache.org/download-connectors.cgi 들어가서<br />\ntar.gz 파일 우클릭 후 링크복사 한다.<br />\n그 후 wget으로 다운<br />\nwget http://mirror.navercorp.com/apache/tomcat/tomcat-connectors/jk/tomcat-connectors-1.2.46-src.tar.gz<br />\ntar -zxvf tomcat-connectors-1.2.46-src.tar.gz<br />\ncd /home/tomcat-connectors-1.2.46-src/native<br />\nfind / -name &#39;apxs&#39; 명령어를 통해 apxs 파일의 위치를 확인한다. 없을경우 yum install httpd-devel<br />\n&nbsp;./configure --with-apxs=/usr/bin/apxs 에러날경우엔 yum install gcc<br />\n이래도 에러날경우엔 apxs 파일에서 맨윗줄 경로확인. #! /usr/bin/perl -w 이렇게 있어야함. 이건안해도되는듯.<br />\n그 후 make 입력 후 make install 입력<br />\ncd /etc/httpd/modules 들어가서 mod_jk.so 있는지 확인</p>\n\n<p>그 후 톰캣서버에 들어가서 포트 확인<br />\n&lt;!-- Define an AJP 1.3 Connector on port 8009 --&gt;<br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;Connector port=&quot;8009&quot; protocol=&quot;AJP/1.3&quot; redirectPort=&quot;8443&quot; /&gt;<br />\n이렇게돼있으면 8009 라는 뜻.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><br />\ncd /etc/httpd/conf<br />\nvi workers.properties</p>\n\n<p>worker.list=worker1<br />\nworker.worker1.type=ajp13&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;# AJP1.3 프로토콜을 사용<br />\nworker.worker1.host=localhost&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;# 톰캣은 local에서 돌고 있습니다.<br />\nworker.worker1.port=8009&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;# 연결할 톰캣의 포트 번호</p>\n\n<p>저장</p>\n\n<p>vi httpd.conf</p>\n\n<p><br />\n(LoadMoudle를 검색하여 맨 마지막에 모듈을 추가)<br />\nLoadModule jk_module &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;modules/mod_jk.so</p>\n\n<p>(파일 맨 아래에 추가)</p>\n\n<p>&lt;IfModule mod_jk.c&gt;<br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; JkWorkersFile /etc/httpd/conf/workers.properties<br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; JkLogFile /home/tomcat-connectors-1.2.48-src/native/apache-2.0/mod_jk.log<br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; JkLogLevel info<br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; JkLogStampFormat &quot;[%a %b %d %H:%M:%S %Y]<br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; JkShmFile /home/tomcat-connectors-1.2.48-src/native/apache-2.0/mod_jk.shm<br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; JkMount /*.jsp worker1<br />\n&lt;/IfModule&gt;</p>\n\n<p>경로 맞춰줘야함. 파일은 없어도 알아서 만들어주는듯.</p>\n\n<p>그 후 테스트 진행.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n도메인 연결은 server.xml 에다가 이렇게 하면 된다.<br />\n&lt;Host name=&quot;dealer.himsintl.com&quot; &nbsp;appBase=&quot;webapps&quot; unpackWARs=&quot;true&quot; autoDeploy=&quot;true&quot;&gt;<br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;Context docBase=&quot;dealer&quot; path=&quot;&quot; reloadable=&quot;true&quot; /&gt;<br />\n&lt;/Host&gt;</p>\n\n<p>httpd.conf 에는</p>\n\n<p>&lt;VirtualHost *:80&gt;<br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp; ServerAdmin musign@musign.net<br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp; DocumentRoot /usr/local/tomcat/webapps/dealer<br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp; ServerName dealer.himsintl.com<br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp; JkMount /*.jsp worker1<br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp; JkMount /*.do worker1<br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp; JkMount /* worker1<br />\n&lt;/VirtualHost&gt;</p>\n\n<p>SSL도 설치할거면<br />\nssl.conf 에다가</p>\n\n<p>&lt;VirtualHost *:443&gt;<br />\n&nbsp; ServerName dealer.himsintl.com<br />\n&nbsp; ServerAlias dealer.himsintl.com<br />\n&nbsp; DocumentRoot /usr/local/tomcat/webapps/dealer</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; SSLEngine on<br />\n&nbsp; SSLProtocol all -SSLv2 -SSLv3 -TLSv1 -TLSv1.1<br />\n&nbsp; SSLCipherSuite ALL:!ADH:!EXPORT:!SSLv2:RC4+RSA:+HIGH:+MEDIUM:+LOW</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; ## 위에서 생성한 SSL 인증서와 개인키<br />\n&nbsp; SSLCertificateFile /etc/httpd/conf.d/ssl/dealer_himsintl_com/cert.pem<br />\n&nbsp; SSLCertificateKeyFile /etc/httpd/conf.d/ssl/dealer_himsintl_com/key.pem<br />\n&nbsp; SSLCACertificateFile /etc/httpd/conf.d/ssl/dealer_himsintl_com/RapidsslDigiCert-Newchain.pem</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; ##<br />\n&nbsp; &lt;Files ~ &quot;.(cgi|shtml|phtml|php3?)$&quot;&gt;<br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; SSLOptions +StdEnvVars<br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;/Files&gt;<br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;Directory &quot;/var/www/cgi-bin&quot;&gt;<br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; SSLOptions +StdEnvVars<br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;/Directory&gt;<br />\n&nbsp; SetEnvIf User-Agent &quot;.*MSIE.*&quot; nokeepalive ssl-unclean-shutdown<br />\n&nbsp; ErrorLog logs/example.com-ssl_error_log<br />\n&nbsp; TransferLog logs/example.com-ssl_access_log<br />\n&nbsp; LogLevel warn<br />\n&nbsp; CustomLog logs/example.com-ssl_request_log <br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp;&quot;%t %h %{SSL_PROTOCOL}x %{SSL_CIPHER}x &quot;%r&quot; %b&quot;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; JkMount /*.jsp worker1<br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp; JkMount /*.do worker1<br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp; JkMount /* worker1<br />\n&lt;/VirtualHost&gt;</p>\n\n<p>이렇게 설정</p>\n','20200714163057'),(43,'Apache 확장자없는 페이지 접근허용','<p>&lt;Directory &quot;/var/www/html&quot;&gt;<br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp; #<br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp; # Possible values for the Options directive are &quot;None&quot;, &quot;All&quot;,<br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp; # or any combination of:<br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp; # &nbsp; Indexes Includes FollowSymLinks SymLinksifOwnerMatch ExecCGI MultiViews<br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp; #<br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp; # Note that &quot;MultiViews&quot; must be named *explicitly* --- &quot;Options All&quot;<br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp; # doesn&#39;t give it to you.<br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp; #<br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp; # The Options directive is both complicated and important. &nbsp;Please see<br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp; # http://httpd.apache.org/docs/2.4/mod/core.html#options<br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp; # for more information.<br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp; #<br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp; Options Indexes FollowSymLinks</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; #<br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp; # AllowOverride controls what directives may be placed in .htaccess files.<br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp; # It can be &quot;All&quot;, &quot;None&quot;, or any combination of the keywords:<br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp; # &nbsp; Options FileInfo AuthConfig Limit<br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp; #<br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp; AllowOverride All</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; #<br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp; # Controls who can get stuff from this server.<br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp; #<br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp; Require all granted<br />\n&lt;/Directory&gt;</p>\n\n<p>밑에서 7번째줄처럼</p>\n\n<p>AllowOverride All 로 변경</p>\n','20200714163118'),(44,'네임서버 셋팅','<p>yum -y install bind-*</p>\n\n<p>vi /etc/named.conf 들어가서<br />\n------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\noptions {<br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; listen-on port 53 { any; };<br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; listen-on-v6 port 53 { ::any; };<br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; directory &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &quot;/var/named&quot;;<br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; dump-file &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &quot;/var/named/data/cache_dump.db&quot;;<br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; statistics-file &quot;/var/named/data/named_stats.txt&quot;;<br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; memstatistics-file &quot;/var/named/data/named_mem_stats.txt&quot;;<br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; allow-query &nbsp; &nbsp; { any; };<br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; recursion yes;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; dnssec-enable yes;<br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; dnssec-validation yes;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; /* Path to ISC DLV key */<br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; bindkeys-file &quot;/etc/named.iscdlv.key&quot;;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; managed-keys-directory &quot;/var/named/dynamic&quot;;<br />\n};<br />\n------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</p>\n\n<p>이런식으로 any 들어간거 3가지 셋팅</p>\n\n<p>vi /etc/named.rfc1912.zones 들어가서</p>\n\n<p>---------------------------------------------<br />\nzone &quot;auntieannes.co.kr&quot; IN {<br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; type master;<br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; file &quot;auntieannes.co.kr.zone&quot;;<br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; allow-update { none; };<br />\n};<br />\n---------------------------------------------</p>\n\n<p>이렇게 추가</p>\n\n<p>cd /var/named</p>\n\n<p>cp named.empty auntieannes.co.kr.zone</p>\n\n<p>named-checkzone auntieannes.co.kr auntieannes.co.kr.zone</p>\n\n<p>chown .named auntieannes.co.kr.zone</p>\n\n<p><br />\nvi auntieannes.co.kr.zone 들어가서</p>\n\n<p>-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n$TTL 3H<br />\n@ &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; IN SOA &nbsp;@ rname.invalid. (<br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 0 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; ; serial<br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 1D &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;; refresh<br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 1H &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;; retry<br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 1W &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;; expire<br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 3H ) &nbsp; &nbsp;; minimum</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; IN &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;NS &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;ns.auntieannes.co.kr.<br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; IN &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;TXT &nbsp; &nbsp; &quot;v=spf1 ip4:222.122.203.159 ~all&quot;<br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; IN &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;A &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 222.122.203.159<br />\nwww &nbsp; &nbsp; IN &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;A &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 222.122.203.159<br />\nns &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;IN &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;A &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 222.122.203.159<br />\nns1 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;IN &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;A &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 222.122.203.159<br />\nns2 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;IN &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;A &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 222.122.203.159<br />\n-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------</p>\n\n<p>이렇게 셋팅</p>\n\n<p>named-checkzone auntieannes.co.kr auntieannes.co.kr.zone 이걸로 확인</p>\n\n<p>그후 service named restart</p>\n','20200714163217'),(45,'DB 커넥션 증가','<p>set global max_connections=3000;</p>\n','20200714163520');
